OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEngland's gardeners face   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpeat compost ban in 2024   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sales of peat to amateur gardeners will
OL,6, be banned in England from 2024, the    
OL,7, government has confirmed.              
OL,9,FThe move follows a consultation and is 
OL,10,Fpart of a pledge to restore peat lands.
OL,12,FThese wild, boggy places are sometimes 
OL,13,Freferred to as the UK's rainforests,   
OL,14,Fbecause of their ability to soak up    
OL,15,Fvast quantities of carbon.             
OL,17,FWhen peat dries out it emits rather    
OL,18,Fthan stores greenhouse gases,          
OL,19,Fcontributing to climate change.        
